262
00:26:11,612 --> 00:26:13,698
Pemuda itu bilang apa lagi?

263
00:26:38,514 --> 00:26:39,515
Grug?

264
00:26:40,224 --> 00:26:41,684
Lari saja terus!

265
00:26:41,851 --> 00:26:42,894
Ayo!

266
00:27:02,246 --> 00:27:06,417
Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima...

267
00:27:09,754 --> 00:27:11,047
Enam.

268
00:27:11,881 --> 00:27:13,800
Di mana kita?

269
00:27:13,966 --> 00:27:16,135
Entahlah. Aku tak yakin.

270
00:27:16,302 --> 00:27:18,054
Di bawah.

271
00:27:18,221 --> 00:27:20,473
Tempat yang lebih di bawah.

272
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:23,935
Namun satu hal pasti,
