293
00:28:50,438 --> 00:28:53,024
aku akan cari yang lebih kecil.

294
00:28:54,567 --> 00:28:55,568
Tunggu.

295
00:28:59,447 --> 00:29:00,448
Ayah?

296
00:29:00,781 --> 00:29:02,450
Akan aku tangani.

297
00:29:12,209 --> 00:29:13,669
Ayo, Ayah, hajar mereka!

298
00:29:14,253 --> 00:29:15,588
Kau berhasil mendesak mereka...

299
00:29:15,755 --> 00:29:16,881
Mereka benar-benar...

300
00:29:17,048 --> 00:29:18,382
Aku suka ini.

301
00:29:19,342 --> 00:29:20,343
Ayah, aku punya ide.

302
00:29:20,509 --> 00:29:22,053
Berhentilah berlari
ke tinju mereka.

303
00:29:23,596 --> 00:29:26,140
Grug, setelah kau selesai,
kita harus pergi.

304
00:29:31,562 --> 00:29:34,523
Benar.
Kau tak bisa mengalahkanku!

305
00:29:55,002 --> 00:29:56,629
Panjat! Panjat!

306
